'''关木通属'''（学名：''Isotrema''）是[[胡椒目|胡椒目]][[马兜铃科|马兜铃科]]下的一个属。原为[[对药马兜铃亚属|对药马兜铃亚属]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Zhu |first1=Xin-Xin |last2=Li |first2=Xiao-Qin |last3=Liao |first3=Shuai |last4=Du |first4=Cheng |last5=Wang |first5=Yuan |last6=Wang |first6=Zhang-Hua |last7=Yan |first7=Jing |last8=Zuo |first8=Yun-Juan |last9=Ma |first9=Jinshuang |title=Reinstatement of Isotrema, a new generic delimitation of Aristolochia subgen. Siphisia (Aristolochiaceae) |journal=Phytotaxa |date=2019-04-10 |volume=401 |issue=1 |pages=1 |doi=10.11646/phytotaxa.401.1.1}}</ref>。

花被管膝曲, 檐部各式, 常3裂; 合蕊柱顶端3裂, 裂片稀再裂; 花药成对与蕊柱裂片对生,果由上而下开裂<ref name="biods.2019183">{{cite journal |last1=Xinxin |first1=Zhu |last2=Jun |first2=Wang |last3=Shuai |first3=Liao |last4=Jinshuang |first4=Ma |title=Synopsis of Aristolochia L. and Isotrema Raf. (Aristolochiaceae) in China |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019-10-20 |volume=27 |issue=10 |pages=1143 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019183}}</ref>。

